videos.headline: Nick Fitzgerald easily runs in 1-yard TD
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald brings in a 1-yard touchdown to give Mississippi State a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Wildcats' Baker 23-yard catch leads to TD
videos.description: Kentucky's Dorian Baker hauls in a 23-yard catch and later Snell Jr. scores a 2-yard rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: Conrad makes leaping catch over defender to setup Kentucky TD
videos.description: Kentucky's CJ Conrad climbs the ladder over defender for a beautiful 23-yard catch.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Snell scores 2nd TD
videos.description: Wildcats RB Benny Snell Jr. comes out in Wildcat formation and punches in a 1-yard TD.

videos.headline: Miss. State Cole intercepts Wildcats' Wilson
videos.description: Brian Cole picks off the Wildcats' QB Terry Wilson, giving good field position to the Bulldogs.

videos.headline: Ajian's interception sets up Kentucky TD
videos.description: Mississppi State QB Nick Fitzgerald gets picked off by Kentucky's Tyrell  Ajian, who returns for 35 yards into Bulldogs territory.

videos.headline: Snell sets Kentucky TD record
videos.description: Kentucky's Benny Snell Jr. erupts for a 36-yard touchdown run, his 38th career touchdown, which is a new school record.

videos.headline: Snell scores 4th TD of the night
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. finds a hole and runs for 23-yard touchdown, his fourth of the night.

videos.headline: Snell runs in 4 TDs, becomes UK TD leader
videos.description: Wildcats' Benny Snell Jr. runs in four touchdowns on 168 yards and becomes Kentucky's all-time touchdown leader with 38, passing Randall Cobb.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Snell runs in 4 TDs, becomes UK TD leader) 2018/9/22 ESHEET
